text: José Antonio de la Torre Delgado (20 April 1987 – 5 December 2024) was a Spanish actor. He was most known as Iván of the Netflix-series Toy Boy. A Spanish thriller about a stripper who tries to prove his innocence. He also played in Amar es para siempre (2013-2024), Vis a vis: El Oasis (2020) and Servir y proteger (2017-2023). He revealed in June 2024 that he was suffering from a serious illness. He died in Montilla on 5 December 2024, at the age of 37. ==References== Category:Spanish television actors Category:1987 births Category:2024 deaths
title: José de la Torre
